<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <title>DCHEQS 2nd Reminder Normal</title>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <style type="text/css">
        @page {
            size: A4;
            font-family: EmbCenturyGothic;
            margin-left: 50px;
            margin-right: 50px;
            margin-top: 25mm;

            @top-left {
                content: element(header);
            }
        }

        body {
            font-family: EmbCenturyGothic;
            font-size: 10pt;
            text-align: justify;
        }

        header {
            text-align: left;
            position: running(header);
            width: 677px;
            margin-left: 7.5px;
        }

        .first-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .first-table td {
            padding-left: 6px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .firstColWidth {
            width: 35%;
        }

        .secondColWidth {
            width: 5%;
            text-align: center;
            font-family: EmbCenturyGothicBold;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .second-table {
            width: 80%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-left: 50px;
        }

        .second-table td {
            padding-left: 6px;
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        .leftPadding {
            padding-left: 6px;
        }

        .fontBold {
            font-family: EmbCenturyGothicBold;
            font-weight: normal;
        }

        .break {
            word-wrap: break-word;
            white-space: normal;
            overflow-wrap: break-word;
        }

        .page-break {
            page-break-before: always;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body style="margin-top: 0px;">
    <header style="font-size: 8pt;margin-top: 50px;">
        <div>
          <img src="${contextVariables.bankIslamLogo!}" alt="bank_islam_logo" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 5px; width:216px; height:50px;display: inline-block "/>
          
            <p style="
            margin-left: 10px;
            display: inline-block;
            vertical-align: middle;
            line-height: 1.1;
          ">
                Jika tidak sampai, sila kembalikan kepada :-<br />
                <span style="white-space: nowrap">
                    P.O. Box 12176, 50724 Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia
                </span>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div>
            <p style="
            margin-top: 5px;
            margin-left: 5px;
            line-height: 1.2;
          ">
                SULIT &amp; PERSENDIRIAN<br />
                Untuk dibuka oleh Penerima sahaja
            </p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <main>
        <p class="leftPadding fontBold" style="padding-top: 40px;">PRIVATE &amp; CONFIDENTIAL</p>
        <table class="first-table">
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Date</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">1.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Customer’s Name</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">2.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Address</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">3.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Current Account No.</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">4.</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="leftPadding">
            <p>Assalamualaikum / Greetings,</p>
            <p>Y.Bhg. Dato’ Sri / Datin Sri / Dato’ / Datuk / Datin/ Encik / Tuan /Puan,</p>
            <div class="fontBold">FINAL REMINDER: DISHONOURED CHEQUE DUE TO INSUFFICIENT FUNDS</div>
            <div style="border: 1px solid;"></div>
            <p>We refer to the above matter and our letter dated 5.</p>
            <p>Please be informed that we are unable to honour the following cheque(s) due to insufficient funds / balances in your account:-</p>
            <table class="second-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="firstColWidth fontBold">Cheque No.</td>
                    <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                    <td class="break">6.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="firstColWidth fontBold" style="width: 40%;">Date of Dishonoured Cheque</td>
                    <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                    <td class="break">7.</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p>Please be reminded that you are required to maintain a sufficient funds in the account at all times before issuing any cheque payments or perform any fund transfer. </p>
            <p>Please take note that if another cheque is returned due to insufficient fund within a year from 8. we may close your account. </p>
            <p>Should you need further clarification, please contact the nearest Bank Islam branch. Your co-operation in this matter would be highly appreciated. Thank you. </p>
            <p>Yours faithfully,</p>
            <br />
            <div class="fontBold">BANK ISLAM MALAYSIA BERHAD</div>
            <div class="break">9.</div>
            <p>No signature required, system generated.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="page-break"></div>

        <p class="leftPadding fontBold" style="padding-top: 40px;">SULIT DAN PERSENDIRIAN </p>
        <table class="first-table">
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Tarikh</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">1.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Nama Pelanggan</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">2.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">Alamat</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">3.</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
                <td class="firstColWidth">No. Akaun Semasa</td>
                <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                <td class="break">4.</td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <div class="leftPadding">
            <p>Assalamualaikum / Salam Sejahtera,</p>
            <p>Y.Bhg. Dato’ Sri / Datin Sri / Dato’ / Datuk / Datin / Encik / Tuan /Puan,</p>
            <div class="fontBold">PERINGATAN TERAKHIR: CEK TAK LAKU DISEBABKAN BAKI TIDAK MENCUKUPI</div>
            <div style="border: 1px solid;"></div>
            <p>Merujuk kepada perkara di atas dan surat kami bertarikh 5.</p>
            <p>Sila ambil maklum bahawa kami tidak dapat menjelaskan cek yang dikeluarkan seperti yang dinyatakan di bawah disebabkan baki akaun anda tidak mencukupi:- </p>
            <table class="second-table">
                <tr>
                    <td class="firstColWidth fontBold">No. Cek</td>
                    <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                    <td class="break">6.</td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td class="firstColWidth fontBold" style="width: 40%;">Tarikh Cek Tak Laku</td>
                    <td class="secondColWidth">:</td>
                    <td class="break">7.</td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <p>Sila ambil peringatan bahawa anda perlu memastikan baki akaun adalah mencukupi pada setiap masa sebelum mengeluarkan sebarang cek pembayaran atau melakukan pindahan wang.</p>
            <p>Sila ambil perhatian sekiranya perkara ini berulang dalam tempoh setahun dari tarikh 8. pihak Bank akan menutup akaun anda tanpa sebarang notis.</p>
            <p>Untuk sebarang pertanyaan, bolehlah menghubungi cawangan Bank Islam yang terdekat. Kerjasama anda di dalam perkara ini amat kami hargai. Terima kasih.</p>
            <p>Yang benar,</p>
            <br />
            <div class="fontBold">BANK ISLAM MALAYSIA BERHAD</div>
            <div class="break">9.</div>
            <p>Ini adalah dokumen cetakan komputer, tiada tandatangan diperlukan.</p>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>
</html>